<a href="http://www.fark.com"title="Fark" target="_blank">Fark</a>.</p>
<a href="#top">top</a> <hr />
<br />
<strong>What if I want to share a Linkpage, but not some Links on it?</strong><a name="PrivateLink"></a>
<p>You have the option of marking individual Links as Private. When marked as Private, Links will not be displayed to anyone viewing the Linkpage except for you.</p>

